review_title: Bought these due to pregnancy related growth.
reviews: Bought these due to pregnancy related growth. My wife says "Comfortable support without an underwire" she also says "my eyes are up here"
product_name: YIANNA Women’s Maternity Nursing Bra Breathable Wireless Breastfeeding Bra 3PACK

reviews:
Pros:
1) great value - you get three bras for the cost of one nursing bra
2) extenders included
3) soft, stretchy and comfortable material

Cons:
1) padding gets in the way when you unhook to nurse especially if you use disposable nursing pads; I removed them
2) not low cut so bra is visible under scoop neck or v-neck shirts
3) the latch to unhook while nursing doesn't click and unclick as easily as other nursing bras but still doable (and ok given the price)

I haven't washed them yet so not sure how they hold up in the wash but I'm pleased with them otherwise.
product_name: YIANNA Women’s Maternity Nursing Bra Breathable Wireless Breastfeeding Bra 3PACK

reviews:
I measure 31 inches under the bust, and 37 inches around the fullest part of the bust.

I purchased the "small" size.

Fits very well; not perfectly, but well.

Similar to the bras you can buy at Motherhood or Thyme.

Very stretchy. Seems small at first look, but stretches to fit.

Supports pretty well for a bra with no underwire.

90% Nylon; 10% Spandex: so not very breathable, but that was expected.

My problem is finding a band that is small enough that it will still fit if the bra stretches. I have to wear this one on the smallest hook for a secure fit, so this bra probably won't fit well after time goes by and it stretches out.

Some of the stiching is not perfect, but overall it is a great buy for the price!
product_name: YIANNA Women’s Maternity Nursing Bra Breathable Wireless Breastfeeding Bra 3PACK

reviews: I am now a 38DDD from pregnancy and I ordered a size L in this as other reviews had mentioned sizing down for a more lifted look. It fits me great and is actually a bra I can stand to wear all day long. My other bra was digging into the top of my belly and making a big red mark. The nipple cover pads look a bit odd on the actual bra, but with a shirt on they look fine and at least nipples arent showing through as the material is thinner than a regular bra. My boobs look normal too as though I am wearing a normal bra and not saggy or anything. I also added the extenders to the back for a more comfy fit. Really happy with my purchase and wish I got these sooner.
product_name: YIANNA Women’s Maternity Nursing Bra Breathable Wireless Breastfeeding Bra 3PACK

reviews: I like this product. The material is good, I feel like it’s a little smaller then I expected, the straps and around my waist is the good size but I feel like the cups are smaller. The padding inside makes my boobs look a little more cone shaped then I like and the beige and pink one i can see the padding threw a little. I prefer the black one. Overall it will do.
product_name: YIANNA Women’s Maternity Nursing Bra Breathable Wireless Breastfeeding Bra 3PACK

review_title: Better than I expected - very comfortable!
reviews: I ordered these as a sleeping bra because I'm now about 5 months pregnant and my chest hurts too much to leave it unsupported at night. I went from a 32 B to about 34 D, so this phenomenon was really new to me! I expected these to be cheaply made and perhaps not that flattering, but was willing to try them for the price. I was pleasantly surprised: they fit really well and feel so comfortable. Construction looks good and there are no loose threads or poorly sewn seams. The inserts are firm enough to give a nice shape too. I've been wearing them non stop for a month now and I'll probably get another set - goodbye uncomfortable underwires!
product_name: YIANNA Women’s Maternity Nursing Bra Breathable Wireless Breastfeeding Bra 3PACK

reviews: Fit exactly as expected. Stretchy and super comfortable and a great price. I bought near the end of pregnancy since none of my bras fit anymore, they worked great with the cups in during the end of pregnancy. When my milk came in and as a result my cup size increased the bra stayed comfortable and still fit. I found with nursing I had to continuously adjust the included cups so I ended up taking them out (hence the loss in star). Much easier to use for nursing without the included cups.
product_name: YIANNA Women’s Maternity Nursing Bra Breathable Wireless Breastfeeding Bra 3PACK

review_title: Honest Review with pros and cons
reviews: Firstly, the item came pretty quickly. It was true to the photo and pretty good quality. I got a size small which is my pregnancy size, but at the moment currently 32 weeks. I also know the material will stretch over time, but initially it fits snug around the band. I found it a tiny bit uncomfortable to wear for extended period of time only because I am pregnant. But it is exactly what I was looking for and post partum I know I will appreciate the tight fit. A tad small in the bust but very stretchy material. Once broken in should be comfortable. Hopefully will fit once I start breastfeeding because of the change in size. Overall definitely recommend!! And I will probably be purchasing more.
product_name: YIANNA Women’s Maternity Nursing Bra Breathable Wireless Breastfeeding Bra 3PACK

review_title: ONLY ORDER FROM THIS SELLER REST R FAKE
reviews:
I AM IN LOVE WITH THESE BRAS AND HOW SUPER SOFT AND COMFORTABLE THESE ARE. I HAD ORDER FROM 2 DIFFERENT COMPANIES AND HAD REALLY ODD SIZES IN PACK OF 3 2 WERE X- SMALL AND 1 WAS MEDIUM RETURN THAT, 2ND COMPANY WAS THE HOOK STAP AROUND CORNER THE EDGES WERE SHARP AND I COUDLNT WEAR MORE THEN 2 MINUTES AND I TRIED 6 TIME BEFORE END UP RETURNING THAT AND BUYING FROM THIS YANAN SELLER.

ONLY CON THE PINK BRA WHEN YOU WASH IT WILL DRAW OUT COLOR SO WASH IT WITH BLACK OR SOAK IT IN WATER WHEN YOU GET IT. I HAD RUIN 3 OF MY WHITE TOPS. :( BUT AGAIN I AM BUYING AGAIN FROM THIS SELLER

PS:MY CAPS LOCK IS BROKEN LOL
product_name: YIANNA Women’s Maternity Nursing Bra Breathable Wireless Breastfeeding Bra 3PACK

reviews:
I'm 40DD now (omg) so I got XL as per size chart, and they're a bit big. Still super comfortable, but I would have preferred L, especially because they come with extenders. They don't shrink in the dryer.

But they're amazing. Comfortable, hold everything together, and have held up perfectly so far in the washer & dryer. I bought these for lounging around the house, but if I had an L with a bit more lift, I wouldn't be very motivated to ever switch to my underwire 'outside' bra.
product_name: YIANNA Women’s Maternity Nursing Bra Breathable Wireless Breastfeeding Bra 3PACK

review_title: Ended up getting size M as I'm still "growing" and M fits me better. I did try the S and it was ...
reviews: I'm currently 16 weeks and was a 34A before pregnancy. Ended up getting size M as I'm still "growing" and M fits me better. I did try the S and it was tight. Unless I use the extender. But just to be safe, I kept the size M since I might keep growing. The material seems good. There are some loose threads here and there but that's not a big deal given the good price. I would recommend it. Don't know how well these are for nursing as I still have a long way to go.
product_name: YIANNA Women’s Maternity Nursing Bra Breathable Wireless Breastfeeding Bra 3PACK

review_title: After a few months of daily wear these aren't holding up so great
reviews: I have worn these everyday for 6 months. They got very stretched out after the first month or two. I can only wear the same one for 3 days then have to switch to the next one and wash to get it to shrink back down. Its the band around the back that gets too stretched out. Then after 4 months the fabric on the outsides of the pads that fit into the bra started peeling off of the pad which is itself sticky. So once that layer of fabric is gone it is very difficult to rearrange the pad inside the bra (cause it sticks and bunches inside the bra pocket). They are however very comfy and very practical. But there are probably better quality options out there. I am a 36DD wearing an XL.
product_name: YIANNA Women’s Maternity Nursing Bra Breathable Wireless Breastfeeding Bra 3PACK

reviews: I ended up returning this product as it was just too small. I ordered an XL and normally wear a 36DDD pre-pregnancy and have been wearing a 38DD while pregnant. It was unfortunately just too snug that it was causing the straps to flip at the back and fall off. The bralette itself is quite stretch so while I thought I could make it work, it was the straps flipping that made it too inconvenient. To get them to stop flipping I had to tighten the straps a lot and then they dug into my shoulders too much. Wish there was one size larger for those who are quite busty.
product_name: YIANNA Women’s Maternity Nursing Bra Breathable Wireless Breastfeeding Bra 3PACK

reviews:
Ordered these because nursing bras are stupid expensive and just needed something without an underwire.
Loved them while nursing my first child, they are basically a sports bra/sleep bra and I wore them day in and out. Loved how I didn’t have to get a new bra every time my supply increased.
Wore them my entire second pregnancy and still wearing them to nurse baby no. 2.
The pads have been wreaked with so much washing and drying but I use nursing pads anyways so it makes no difference to me.
Don’t wear them as an everyday bra now, more for sleeping, but I definitely still could!
product_name: YIANNA Women’s Maternity Nursing Bra Breathable Wireless Breastfeeding Bra 3PACK

reviews: Very comfortable. Easy snaps when finished nursing. Dislike that the straps are too close to the side of my body as opposed to being set in further. The straps sometimes fall down because of this. The padding is aweful though. A different material would be better; one that is more flexible when you need to nurse. It gets bunches up inside and difficult to get smoothed back out before snapping the clip.
product_name: YIANNA Women’s Maternity Nursing Bra Breathable Wireless Breastfeeding Bra 3PACK

reviews: These have little to no structure and the clasps are hard to undo with one hand. The straps are so far off to the side on the back of the bra that the straps fall down my shoulders constantly. I had to cut them and sew them closer to the clasp in the back. Only upside is they have removable pads for the leakage and they're very soft and not too bad to sleep in.
product_name: YIANNA Women’s Maternity Nursing Bra Breathable Wireless Breastfeeding Bra 3PACK

reviews:
I bought these based off the good reviews it received however they didn't quite live up to my expectations. After the first wash, 2 had gotten destroyed, the clasps had broken off deeming it useless to use for nursing. I have 1 left which I've been using and that has been fine so far.

Wish it were better quality, but besides that, in terms of size, I'm a medium and I bought medium and the fit was perfect. It's soft and comfortable to wear. I hope you have better luck with them than I did!
product_name: YIANNA Women’s Maternity Nursing Bra Breathable Wireless Breastfeeding Bra 3PACK

reviews: Good value but fits extremely small. I'm a medium and ordered large but it was still too small. Bands roll and do not sit flat. Having said that, I have paid more for brand-name nursing bras that aren't any better.

It also did not come with the bra extenders for all three bras so I couldn't even try and see what it would have felt like if it even fit a little. Pretty bummed. Returned the product, still waiting for Amazon to credit the amount back.
product_name: YIANNA Women’s Maternity Nursing Bra Breathable Wireless Breastfeeding Bra 3PACK

After washing them before wearing(delicate cycle) thread started coming out around the band. the material is leaving flakes behind on me which the baby could ingest if I don’t notice them before feeding....

reviews:
I'm a 40DD and reading the reviews I really wasn't sure if these would fit or not but I figured I'd give it a try considering the affordability. I'm glad I did! I got the largest size available.
They fit so nicely around the band, it doesn't dig into your skin at all. The material is stretchy so there's room for engorgement. They do have those triangular inserts in the inner lining (like some swimsuits do) but if you don't like them you can take them out. There is a slit to do so.
I just wish I had bought these sooner! They would have been awesome to have in the hospital when babybear was born as they don't have an underwire but are still nice and supportive.
They look good under a tshirt and they are awesome to sleep in.
I would recommend this product and I would repurchase in the future!
product_name: YIANNA Women’s Maternity Nursing Bra Breathable Wireless Breastfeeding Bra 3PACK

reviews:
These bras are decent for the price. I am something like a 32 e and these bras have decent support. I probably should have gone for a medium for the band size, but I was concerned that the cups wouldn't fit, so I went for large. I am sure there are more supporting nursing bras out there, but it would also be double the price.
I tightened the straps and I found it comfortable and not too bouncy.
Some extra threads here and there but nothing that you don't find in clothing. It didn't affect function.
I took out the molded cups because I found they folded into the pocket when I was nursing and also because my boobs are just a bit too big that it is noticeable.
product_name: YIANNA Women’s Maternity Nursing Bra Breathable Wireless Breastfeeding Bra 3PACK

reviews: Amazing product ladies! If yer looking for something buy these! Life saver. I'm from nwt canada and a 40DD. Had 2 thyme maternity bras and one broke. Very expensive too! So ordered these up since I was down to one bra and no bras for my size in town let alone nursing ones. They are super comfy. And they support awesome! Slept in them and everything. Each color works for whatever u wanna wear really (minus some summer dresses) but honestly! Read another 40DD review on here and that's what encouraged me. Thank god for that woman's note! Buy buy buy!!!! Oh! And took only 2 weeks to get here so damn fast!!!!! Was amazing!!!
product_name: YIANNA Women’s Maternity Nursing Bra Breathable Wireless Breastfeeding Bra 3PACK
